  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the robata grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Roll out the lamination-puff pastry sheet to a 30x30cm square and place on parchment.",
    "Spread a thin layer of tomato sauce over the pastry, leaving a small border.",
    "Sprinkle the shredded sweet cabbage evenly over the sauce.",
    "Drizzle with olive oil and sprinkle minced garlic, salt, pepper, and smoked paprika.",
    "Add dollops of vegan mozzarella and a handful of fresh dill.",
    "Cook the pizza on the robata grill for 10 to 12 minutes, until the pastry is golden and the cheese is melted.",
    "Remove, let rest for 2 minutes, then slice and serve hot with a squeeze of lemon zest."
